<lb/>Adjutant Gen<hi rend="underline"><hi rend="sup">l</hi></hi> U. S. A.
<lb/>Washington
<lb/>General:</p>
<p>I am instructed by the Governor to request that Andrew H. Clark late Captain in the 7<hi rend="underline">"</hi> Ky Inf<hi rend="sup">y.</hi> (a resigned Officer) be allowed to be mustered into the U. S. service as Lieut. Col. 47. Ky. Infy.</p>
<p>Resp<hi rend="sup">y</hi>
<lb/>Your obed<hi rend="underline"><hi rend="sup">t</hi></hi> Serv<hi rend="sup">t</hi>
<lb/><hi rend="underline">John Boyle</hi>
<lb/>Adj<hi rend="sup">t</hi> Gen<hi rend="sup">l</hi> of Ky</p>
